s cidades}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11  de ref\u250?gio, Siqu\u233?m e suas pastagens, na regi\u227?o montanhosa de Efraim; tamb\u233?m Gezer e suas pastagens, }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 68}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Jocme\u227?o e suas pastagens, Bete-Horom\u160?e suas pastagens, }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 69}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Aijalom e suas pastagens, e Gate-Rimom e suas pastagens. }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 70}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?E da meia tribo de Manass\u233?s: Aner e suas pastagens, e Bile\u227?o e suas pastagens; essas cidades foram dadas ao restante das fam\u237?lias dos coatitas.\par}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 71}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Os gersonitas receberam da fam\u237?lia da meia tribo de Manass\u233?s: Gol\u227?, em Bas\u227?, e suas pastagens, e Astarote e suas pastagens. }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 72}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?E da tribo de Issacar: Quedes e suas pastagens, Daberate e suas pastagens, }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf10 73}{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp1033\f2\cf11 \u160?Ramote e suas pastagens, e An\u233?m e suas pastagens. }{\rtlch\fcs1\alang1046\af1\ltrch\fcs0\lang1046\langnp1046\langfe1033\langfenp103